{"type":"article","id":7811,"title":"九岁被当街打死的男孩父亲发感谢信","uid":9304,"topics":[2845,455],"contents":"人命不值钱，政府面子最重要。<br>\n<br>\n1月5日，长沙雨花区9岁男孩罗某被殴打致死。9日上午，罗某父亲在微信朋友圈发了一封感谢信，信中感谢多个政府部门以及关心罗某的社会各界人士。罗父告诉<a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%AC%E6%8A%A5?from=feed&amp;loc=at\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@新京报</a>&nbsp;记者，感谢信的确是他发布的，“孩子母亲情绪不稳定，后续所有事宜会委托政府帮忙处理。”<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EI7NZAiXsAAoeGJ?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EI7NZAiXsAAoeGJ?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EI7NZAiXsAAoeGJ?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-11-09","agreeCount":10,"discussionCount":0}